wiki.text:
'Wegert' was an electricals company in Germany which specialized in white goods.
Latterly, Wegert was a wholly owned subsidiary of Kesa Electricals plc, although
most of its lifespan was spent in Kingfisher plc. The stores were closed down in
2003 due to declining sales.
